ji\" />"},{"pid":"5cee73fb3f1bebbc4ab2c4df2b1c5f813d8eb3a3","tid":442792,"uid":4559,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T15:00:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"88e056750c369cbe5b56e27c208972687eee9e0e","tid":442792,"uid":10122,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T15:03:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>1400好似先平香港2，300 做咩要俾你賺 你真係當連登全部小學雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咪就係平 2 300 囉<br />\n你自己都講左點解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n平2, 300個少少都要代購咁弱智<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 重點係仲要俾樓主賺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n應該唔收錢幫連登仔買返黎就最好啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed030b8686dd7da43707587c2c2c1155686040cb","tid":442792,"uid":129925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T15:04:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>好奇一問呢個袋有咩咁特別要賣千四<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我個個用左十年無穿無爛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\non9 我個nike 袋都用左8年  係條咩條少少爛  <br />\n根本好易用十年"},{"pid":"f2c5a018c507b7ed8aa4687f576992245b49b98f","tid":442792,"uid":4559,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T15:07:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"af5776c67fc1548d82379d03e1950b23bb8b4238","tid":442792,"uid":135957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T15:10:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d03ed239a6cc0bf45a5328cef5b7a2a54e4b3153","tid":442792,"uid":10122,"like":0,"dislike":28,"score":-28,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T15:10:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>連登仔會話你買左=1手<br />\n之後放出黎=2手<br />\n所以要平一半架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都真係r爆頭<br />\n首先個背囊唔係假野都可以話呃人<br />\n第二事實係平過香港買（上網原價見係1780），都仲要比人屌<br />\n仲要有on9仔話自己唔完唔要想搵人接貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n已經講明帶返黎有賺錢，依家d連登仔真係好難招呼<br />\n如果咁都可以屌d代購網可以執鳩晒<br />\n仲講咩平200-300仲乜要比你賺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁有人鐘意有平唔買買貴比多d人賺都無辦法嘅"},{"pid":"8193fc918f9abd9c55477aa6e545ac15acb8c056","tid":442792,"uid":10122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T15:12:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>1400好似先平香港2，300 做咩要俾你賺 你真係當連登全部小學雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咪就係平 2 300 囉<br />\n你自己都講左點解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n平2, 300個少少都要代購咁弱智<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 重點係仲要俾樓主賺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n應該唔收錢幫連登仔買返黎就最好啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n冇人叫你咁做 只係覺得咁樣俾錢你賺既人好弱智啫 祝你生意興隆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁你出去買人地唔賺你錢嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b07d344c090c60390e72a79bcec8f06647461ff","tid":442792,"uid":4562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T15:16:52.000Z","msg":"如果出街見到人用 應該就係樓主<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7a051a73813317e3aaced982b624d9051a67916","tid":442792,"uid":10122,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T15:17:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果出街見到人用 應該就係樓主<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n記得見到過黎打招呼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09ab8b39132b7c352d328ca6a7ce12062d7cbd10","tid":442792,"uid":6696,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T15:31:24.000Z","msg":"aeon 8折緊"},{"pid":"90cace9a5123dac09679845722a552b940eef02e","tid":442792,"uid":33338,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T15:34:33.000Z","msg":"樓豬：呢個袋經我柒頭開光二千都唔洗呀"},{"pid":"fd49cee3c07d31b4d6a9fc4d657db212402d92a9","tid":442792,"uid":6696,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T15:41:12.000Z","msg":"aeon 全線<br />\n乜款乜size 都係8折<br />\n應該都係14xx"},{"pid":"cee06b4f72cccbaee5f2a5203f582003e5e45ee9","tid":442792,"uid":53773,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T15:45:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>aeon 全線<br />\n乜款乜size 都係8折<br />\n應該都係14xx</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d6ee5ff19959c40a68b643be7e8bc40ecb2bd68","tid":442792,"uid":10122,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T15:50:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓豬：呢個袋經我柒頭開光二千都唔洗呀</blockquote><br />\n未撚用過點開光呀高手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clow